{"tid":724551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我肯交英國稅","createTime":"2018-07-01T04:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T11:36:55.000Z","uid":64034,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4abf28915cfbf13b86acc69d95b4f09f3fa3704","tid":724551,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"好撚後悔, 97當年18歲 因為bno好撚多人申請, 冇攞到本bno, 仲記得11歲攞身份證嘅時候, 我係揀英國籍的, 如果我肯交英國稅七年, 畀返本bno我得唔得? 攞咗有備無患, 越嚟越覺得香港好撚可怕,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好懷念細個英治時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人正常好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd2c3bc87b9842e0f98ed07060f1b402233a183","tid":724551,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e96ac46a0fa5d50e6e8b37aca20bef067f4dc96","tid":724551,"uid":50328,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56a335abd8f7a89d7f292e145fcc95df04ba2d21","tid":724551,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad46d35b4c24dc808c18fa4cd0c592df6b54e89","tid":724551,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e96ac46a0fa5d50e6e8b37aca20bef067f4dc96","tid":724551,"uid":50328,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"一日最撚衰都係自己, 趕撚 住去旅行走去攞特衰, 我細嗰本passport係黑色㗎, 11歲之前本護照係黐住父母的, 11歲之後就換咗本黑色嘅英國乜七護照, 唔記得咗個名, 跟住叫我哋去換bno以我冇去到, 後悔到今時今日"},{"pid":"3a56272743a2d14450a4e1d77d1f6dd860d66c57","tid":724551,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"我真係知錯啦, 畀我申請返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj